13 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
14 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 26 O.S. 2021, Section 2-101.9, is
15 amended to read as follows:
16 Section 2-101.9. Members of the State Election Board shall be
17 paid Fifty Dollars ($50.00) Seventy-five Dollars ($75.00) per diem
18 for each meeting for the purpose of conducting hearings required by
19 law, and Thirty-five Dollars ($35.00) Seventy-five Dollars ($75.00)
20 per diem for other meetings, and shall be allowed mileage
21 reimbursement at the rate provided by the State Travel Reimbursement
22 Act, Section 500.1 et seq. of Title 74 of the Oklahoma Statutes.
